title: Best free agents & What's more likely!
itunes:title: Best free agents & What's more likely!
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- discuss the latest news from around the league and who are the best free agents still available (25:57). Then the guys play another edition of What's more likely! (37:06).
